@Parcly-Taxel,you shouldn't have pushed to the branch. In general, don't ever push to a branch unless it's yours, or if it's tagged `help-wanted`. The change you have done removing the parentheses doesn't look good, because `k + 1` is a single unit, so it was kept together on purpose.

If you have suggestions to make, the correct way is to suggest these using the github interface, and let the owner of the branch accept them or not.

By the way, thanks a lot for the review, this is much appreciated and very useful!

